interestingcomments.content: Using a Nikon Z50, Tamron 90mm 2.8 Macro, and a Nikon Plan Fluor ELWD 20X microscope objective all mounted to a modified 3D printer, I created this 12,300 x 12,000px panoramic focus stacked image (made up of 750 photos total) of the underside of a tomato leaf.
